    "summary": "The user expresses profound existential despair and dissociation, using metaphors of emptiness and a \"pilotless plane\" to suggest that their life no longer has purpose or value. The assistant responds with empathetic validation of the user's feelings while consistently attempting to redirect the conversation toward professional mental health support and the possibility of finding new meaning.",
